docs.snippet: It now seems fairly certain that Uruguay is going to change her form of government from the Swisstype collegiate system back to the one-man presidential system. The Congress in Montevideo, at a joint session this week, agreed by a comfortable...
docs.lead_paragraph: It now seems fairly certain that Uruguay is going to change her form of government from the Swisstype collegiate system back to the one-man presidential system. The Congress in Montevideo, at a joint session this week, agreed by a comfortable majority on a proposition to be submitted to the electorate Nov. 27.
